<headline>Severe Weather Statement issued September 03 at 11:37PM MDT until September 03 at 11:45PM MDT by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...THE SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WARNING FOR CENTRAL PONDERA...EASTERN
GLACIER AND TOOLE COUNTIES WILL EXPIRE AT 1145 PM MDT...
The storms which prompted the warning have weakened below severe
limits, and no longer pose an immediate threat to life or property.
Therefore, the warning will be allowed to expire.  However gusty
winds are still possible with these thunderstorms.</description>
